description: Extend your control with the UltraPro™ 1-Outlet Indoor Plug-in Dimming Lighting Control with Tether. The convenient device inserts into any indoor outlet for easy operation of plug-in lights. Compatible with dimmable LED, CFL, incandescent and halogen bulbs, the easy-to-use lighting control is perfect for lamps, seasonal lighting and more. The compact design with one side-access polarized outlet fits in tight spaces, such as behind furniture, under tables and more. An integrated push-button tether with 5ft. cord offers unique, enhanced operation. It can also serve as a foot switch for discreet floor placement and features a keyhole on the back to provide additional mounting options. In addition to functioning as an ON/OFF button, the tether offers full-range dimming. When used with dimmable lights, continuously pressing the button adjusts brightness to accommodate every task or occasion. Improve your outlet by leaps and bounds with the UltraPro 1-Outlet Indoor Plug-in Dimming Lighting Control with Tether.
